Title: Regularization Ambiguity Problem for the Chern-Simons Shift
Authors: K. Nittoh and T. Ebihara
Comments: 7 pages, 1 figure, latex 2e, will appear at Mod. Phys. Lett. A
Report-no: CHIBA-EP-86
Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A13 (1998) 2231-2237
\\
  We consider the Chern-Simons parameter shift with the hybrid regularization
consisting of the higher covariant derivative (HCD) and the Pauli-Villars (PV)
regulators. We show that the shift is closely related to the parity of the
regulators and get the shift and no-shift results by a suitable choice of the
PV regulators. A naive treatment of the HCD term leads incorrect value of the
shift.
